*   ## **_Eddie Kingston def. Big Bill_**
    

They botched the finish as Kingston missed his spinning back fist and went for the pinfall anyway.

Post match they try to attack Kingston but Hook comes out to save him. Kingston hits Bryan Keith with a spinnin back fist that has MUCH MORE spice this time.

