*   ## **_AEW Unified Championship: Kazuchika Okada def. Mascara Dorada and Konosuke Takeshita_**
    

MATCH OF THE NIGHT

Okada pins Mascara Dorada with the Rainmaker

Kudos to everyone in that ring 👏🏽👏🏽👏🏽👏🏽

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/2023e0b3-d41f-4617-912d-4cbb1baef563/17609.jpg)

*   ## **_Coffin Match: Jon Moxley def Darby Allin_**
    

Bryan Danielson at one point offered Darby Allin a plastic bag to take ultimate revenge on Jon Moxley.

Darby almost ended Mox but PAC returned and took out Darby. Powerbomb onto a coffin outside of the ring, put into a body bag. Placed in the coffin.

The Death Riders take Darby Allin out in the casket. They are officially back at full power with the return of PAC to their ranks.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/c1d2360a-6b45-44fe-8522-c59e01a5911b/17612.jpg)

Orange Cassidy returns this Wednesday to take on the Don Callis Family with the Conglomeration!!!!

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/e8e81657-1f44-4749-adf3-7d4080a5aeec/processed_17618.jpg)

The Death Riders sent Wheeler Yuta out to give Kris Statlander advice before the Women's World Championship match.

*   ## **_AEW Women's World Championship: Kris Statlander def. Toni Storm(c), Thekla and Jaime Hayter_**
    

She won the belt using Wheeler Yuta's Seatbelt Cradle pinfall. 🤔

