*   ## **_AEW World Championship: Hangman Adam Page def. Kyle Fletcher in a 40 Minute CLASSIC_**
    

Both men utilized the moves of their rivals in an attempt to defeat each other.

In the end, as Hangman predicted, it was not Kyle Fletcher's time.

What an incredible match.

